Default is true.
.TP
.B --force
Allow replacement of an existing non-aerolitctl-generated playbook.
.TP
.B --no-backup
Do not create timestamped backups before changing files.
.TP
.B --dry-run
Preview output without writing files.
.SH KICKSTART OPTIONS
.TP
.I PROFILE
PXE profile id. Optional with
.BR --guided .
.TP
.B --guided
Interactively build a PXE/Kickstart profile.
.TP
.B --guided-show-details
Show template or partial contents during guided choices.
.TP
.B --list-kickstart-options
List discovered profiles, Kickstart templates, and partials.
.TP
.BI --template-root " PATH"
Extra host-visible pxe-content template root to scan. Repeatable.
.TP
.BI --template-source " auto|host|container"
Choose host/container discovery mode. Default:
.BR auto .
.TP
.BI --pxe-content-container " NAME_OR_ID"
Specific running pxe-content container to inspect.
.TP
.BI --container-engine " auto|podman|docker"
Container engine for live pxe-content discovery. Default:
.BR auto .
.TP
.BI --container-template-root " PATH"
Container-side template/profile directory to copy from. Repeatable.
.TP
.BI --template-option " TEMPLATE"
Use a discovered Kickstart template id.
.TP
.BI --partial " TEMPLATE"
Compose a new override template from a discovered partial/template id.
.TP
.BI --from-profile " PROFILE"
Profile to clone when creating a new profile. Default:
.BR minimal .
.TP
.B --reset-from-profile
Rebuild an existing generated profile from
.B --from-profile
before applying options.
.TP
.BI --title " TITLE"
PXE profile title/menu section.
.TP
.BI --label " LABEL"
Alias for
.BR --install-label .
.TP
.BI --install-label " LABEL"
Install label used for generated boot entries.
.TP
.BI --menu-target " TARGET"
iPXE menu target. Defaults to the profile id.
.TP
.BI --os " OS"
Supported OS id. Repeatable or comma-separated.
.TP
.BI --kickstart-template " TEMPLATE"
Relative Kickstart template path consumed by pxe-content.
.TP
.BI --copy-template " PATH"
Copy a local Kickstart template into
.IR /etc/aerolit/overrides/pxe/templates .
.TP
.BI --kernel-arg " ARG"
Append one kernel argument. Repeatable or comma-separated.
.TP
.BI --set-kernel-args " ARGS"
Replace kernel args with this comma-separated list.
.TP
.B --clear-kernel-args
Write an empty kernel argument list before appending values.
.TP
.B --uefi
Enable UEFI boot entries.
.TP
.B --no-uefi
Disable UEFI boot entries.
.TP
.B --bios
Enable legacy BIOS boot entries.
.TP
.B --no-bios
Disable legacy BIOS boot entries.
.TP
.B --implemented
Mark the profile implemented so real boot targets/Kickstarts are generated.
.TP
.B --placeholder
Mark the profile as visible and non-bootable.
.TP
.B --enabled
Show the profile in the generated main PXE menu.
.TP
.B --disabled
Hide the profile from the generated main PXE menu.
.TP
.B --show-in-main-menu
Explicitly show the profile in the main menu.
.TP
.B --hide-from-main-menu
Hide the profile from the main menu.
.TP
.B --no-refresh-generated-vars
Do not refresh
.IR group_vars/all/aerolitctl_pxe_generated.yml .
.TP
.B --validate
Validate managed PXE state after generation.
.TP
.BI --bundle-path " PATH"
Bundle path.
.TP
.B --force
Allow replacement of existing non-aerolitctl-managed output files.
.TP
.B --no-backup
Do not create timestamped backups before changing files.
.TP
.B --dry-run
Preview output without writing files.
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
aerolitctl generate playbook deploy_pxe_content --hosts pxe_server --role aerolit.pxe_content.pxe_content
aerolitctl generate playbook controller_setup --role namespace.collection.prereq --role namespace.collection.configure
aerolitctl generate playbook --guided
aerolitctl generate playbook --list-playbook-roles
aerolitctl generate kickstart rhel9_workstation --from-profile minimal --os rhel9 --label "RHEL 9 Workstation"
aerolitctl generate kickstart --guided
aerolitctl generate pxe-profile small_disk_lab --from-profile small_disk --os rhel9,rhel8 --kernel-arg inst.sshd
.fi
.SH FILES
.TP
.I <bundle>/collections-hub/ansible/*.yml
Generated playbooks.
.TP
.I <bundle>/collections-hub/ansible/group_vars/all/aerolitctl_pxe_generated.yml
Generated PXE variables refreshed by Kickstart generation unless disabled.
.TP
.I /etc/aerolit/overrides/pxe/profiles/PROFILE.yml
Generated PXE profile override.
.TP
.I /etc/aerolit/overrides/pxe/templates
Copied or composed Kickstart template overrides.
.SH NOTES
Generated files include AeroLIT markers. Existing files without the expected
marker are not overwritten unless
