is supplied.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR aerolitctl (1),
.BR aerolitctl-configure (1),
.BR aerolitctl-deploy (1)











.TH AEROLITCTL-LOGS 1 "June 2026" "aerolitctl 0.1.0" "User Commands"
