[\fB--dry-run\fR] [\fB--merge\fR] [\fB--no-backup\fR] [\fB--no-redact-diff\fR] [\fB--verbose\fR]
.I FILE
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B aerolitctl settings
manages the saved YAML settings in
.IR /etc/aerolit/aerolitctl.yml .
