for the selected RHEL major tree.
.TP
.B --restart-affected
Restart affected services where the sync implementation supports it.
.TP
.BI --to " PATH"
Destination path for export-style operations.
.TP
.BI --keep " COUNT"
Retention count for cleanup-style operations.
