.BI --days " DAYS"
Retention age for cleanup-style operations.
.TP
.B --dry-run
Preview the sync plan without writing.
.TP
.B --yes, -y
Answer yes to confirmation prompts.
.TP
.B --force
Allow operations that otherwise require extra confirmation.
.TP
.B --show-files
Show changed files.
.TP
.B --show-all-files
Show all files considered by the plan.
.TP
.B --show-skipped
Show skipped files.
.TP
.BI --diff-lines " N"
Limit diff output lines.
.TP
.BI --path " PATH"
Limit diff/review output to a path.
.TP
.BI --output " text|json|yaml"
Choose output format for supported status/report actions.
.TP
.BI --plan-output " PATH"
Write the generated plan to a file.
.TP
.B --no-backup
Do not back up overwritten or removed
.I collections-hub
files.
.TP
.B --review
Review planned changes.
.TP
.B --review-conflicts
Review conflicts.
.TP
.B --review-removals
Review removals.
.TP
.B --defaults
Use default behavior for supported actions.
.TP
.B --all
Apply to all supported items for supported actions.
.TP
.B --verbose
Show more detailed output.
